rooms.Name: Entrance to the Great Chessboard
rooms.Description:
You find yourself looking up at a huge archway that looks like an entrance
to what appears to be a gigantic chessboard.  Beyond the archway you see a
checkerboard of black and white squares.

rooms.Name: The Black Treasury
rooms.Description:
You are in a dark room that appears to have only one exit - the way you came
in.  You can barely see your hand in front of your face, and as you shuffle
slowly across the floor, you trip over something that sounds metallic on the
floor.  Picking it up, you discover you have found a priceless item.  You
wonder if there may be more.

Exits.Description: The door goes up to a black square.
